      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "I come back up to the common area and finally dive into learning some basic Xhosa phrases. They’re playing reggae, it’s warm in the sunroom - people and dogs lounge about. I book myself in for a Xhosa lesson at 4pm and do some planning for ",
            "link": null
