            "content": "I spend some time chatting with people in the common room. Make a tuna mayo and avo lunch on Salticrax which is truly amazing. I have a coffee with Jemma and Gareth while making jokes about “cool cool” people. I settle into the back of the bakkie for what I realise is my first afternoon nap since Joburg with Jordan. ",
