          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "We head over to the shabeen to buy some beers. We go into the little room next to it first with some people wasted and dancing; the walls bear barring a boom box in the corner. The one wasted dude goes to buy us beers. He walks back and forth between the room and the shabeen, and each time he’s back without beers and slightly less money haha. In the end we go buy the beers ourself down R20 but up one good story.",
