          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Gareth rolls a hash joint that is atomically strong. We start up the foosball table and proceed to have the most exciting game. Me and Gareth against Sheera and Rudy. We start off on top and score 5 goals in quick succession, to which they respond with a comeback and suddenly we both need to score to win. They score an own goal and we claim victory with heart rates dangerously high. I struggle to go to sleep after all that.",
